description: Frozen embryo transfer cycle starting from period day 1. The cycle may be natural or medicated, depending on monitoring, ovulation timing, and medications used.
In vitro fertilisation cycle involving ovarian stimulation, egg retrieval, fertilisation, and embryo transfer or freezing.
Intrauterine insemination cycle with natural or mild stimulation, timed insemination, and luteal support if required.
Fertility preservation cycle involving ovarian stimulation, egg retrieval, and freezing of unfertilised eggs for future use
